 the West and the non-West are challenged through a radical reconfiguration of the geopolitics of knowledge production and consumption.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 0aFilm criticismzJapanxHistoryy20th century. 0aMotion pictureszJapanxAestheticsxHistoryy20th century. 0aMotion pictureszJapanxPhilosophyxHistoryy20th century. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / History & Criticism.2bisacsh  a20th century film criticism.  aavant garde art.  abergsonism.  acinematic realism.  aconsumption.  acultural studies.  adocumentary film.  afilm criticism.  afilm theory.  afilm.  ageopolitics.  ajapan.  ajapanese cinema.  ajapanese film theory.  ajapanese film.  ajapanese movies.  aknowledge production.  aliterary adaptation.  aliterature.  amarxism.  amodernism.  amodernity.  amovie criticism.  amovie theory.  anaturalism.  aphilosophy.  apostwar debates.  arealism and modernism.  atextual realism.  auniversalism and particularism.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertArt and Architecture eBook-Package 2020z978311073823008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2020z9783110704655oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2020 Englishz978311070478508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUC Press Frontlist eBook-Package 2020z978311069041540uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520975903zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520975903423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780520975903.jpg  a978-3-